The paper deals with the practical implementation of a photon-counting receiver in optical scattering communication, which involves signal processing and detection techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves experimental and simulation results, which suggest that it could belong to cs.OH (Other Computer Science), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.PH (Physics), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
